name: Support Manager
query:
SELECT
  "tabSupport EXP"."name" AS "Name",
  "tabSupport EXP"."workflow_state" AS "Status",
  "tabSupport EXP"."project" AS "Project Name",
  "tabSupport EXP"."module" AS "Module Name",
  "tabSupport EXP"."initialtion_datetime" AS "Initiation Datetime",
  "tabSupport EXP"."redmine_url" AS "Redmine ID",
  "tabSupport EXP"."task" AS "Task Type",
  "tabSupport EXP"."description" AS "Task Description",
  "tabSupport EXP"."developer" AS "Assigned Developer",
  "tabSupport EXP"."actual_end_date" AS "Complete Date",
  "tabSupport EXP"."actual_hours" AS "Hours"
  
FROM
  "tabSupport EXP"
